children.value: The updated My Vibe is a flash, an impulse, a charge of energy. It can now reflect your music world!
Its colors and shape depend on tracks in My Collection and the music you're listening to right now.
If you like a track in My Vibe, it'll light up. Try it! And then try to stop.
The new animation is also something you won't be able to take your eyes off. But please do from time to time.
In this update, we learnt to delete and dislike tracks — just to add and like new ones!
You can now delete tracks from your playlists.
Now, when you dislike a track in the player, it immediately moves on to the next track.
The artists' pages now feature the "Known to you" section with the tracks you've already heard in My Vibe or added to your Collection.
"Where on Earth is that playlist? What was its name again?" Don't worry, this will never happen again. All your favorite stuff will always be at hand.

You can now pin anything you like in the left part of the screen: an album, a playlist, an artist, or My Vibe with special settings. Tap the icon in the upper-right corner of the cover to make sure you never lose any of the stuff you like. By the way, you can also pin it via the context menu.
Your playlists now also have Search: use it to look for and add new tracks.

Some are waiting for the new album by Kanye West, some hoping for a new track by Ranetki. We're all different. But waiting for our favorite music has become more convenient for each of us, because now your Collection features a special section for upcoming releases you liked
This release is minor but important. We:
Added the Share button to album and artist screens.
Made the app a bit more accessible for blind and visually impaired users.
Introducing a few updates as everyone seems to be looking for something new for summer.
We've added the Settings section to the profile page. Tips for using hot keys are already there. And it's just the beginning!
We've also added a section with recommended playlists by genre to the home page. Discover new releases and enjoy your favorite music!
Notes in particular order turn into music. And this update is for those who like keeping their playlists in order.
You can now easily rearrange tracks in playlists: just drag them where you want.
We've saved some space in the playlists section in the Collection. All your playlists are now displayed on a single page that's easy to navigate.
We have news, and the news is good!
Added the listening history to the For You section. No track from My Vibe will ever be lost now.
More and more artist sections feature the Donate button. Use this chance to thank artists for their music.
You can now access podcasts from the side menu.
You can now use search to look for podcasts.
The Collection now also features podcasts.
This is the feature Windows users have been waiting for: they can now minimize the application to system tray. Who knows, perhaps someone will make a podcast about it one day?
У этого обновления тема одна: жанры. Точнее, 400+ жанров, которым мы обучили Мою волну. Всё это не просто так, а чтобы вам было легче изучать новые музыкальные направления и открывать редких артистов
Ещё мы добавили персональные жанровые рекомендации в блок «Больше открытий» во вкладке «Для вас»
Во вкладке «Тренды» теперь есть рубрика «Жанр недели» — каждую неделю там будет появляться подборка из 10 жанров в одном из музыкальных направлений
В разделе «Жанры» появился блок «Популярное», а на странице каждого жанра — описание, ключевые представители, тематическая Моя волна и похожие жанры
